INTRODUCCI√ìN LIBRER√çA learnPopGen.

La librer√≠a learnPopGen (Revell et al.¬†2019) permite realizar an√°lisis num√©rico y simulaciones con el prop√≥sito de comprender principios b√°sicos de gen√©tica de poblaciones y evoluci√≥n.

Funciones clave

genetic.drift(): This function simulates genetic drift at a biallelic genetic locus with no selection and no mutation in a sexually reproducing diploid population or set of populations.

founder.event(): This function simulates genetic drift with a founding event / population bottleneck at time etime.

selection(): This function performs numerical analysis of a simple biallelic selection model.

msd: Simulates migration, natural selection, and genetic drift. Selection can be in opposite directions in the two populations experiencing gene flow.
